00:35:29,180 --> 00:35:30,480
el missatge constantment.

1647
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:31,640
Clar,

1648
00:35:31,980 --> 00:35:32,640
ens obliga

1649
00:35:32,640 --> 00:35:33,480
a aturar-nos

1650
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,100
i a demanar

1651
00:35:34,100 --> 00:35:34,700
que l'altre

1652
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:35,700
ens expliqui

1653
00:35:35,700 --> 00:35:37,480
amb les seves pròpies paraules

1654
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:39,120
què redimonis ha entès

1655
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:40,500
per evitar malentesos

1656
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:41,260
que podrien ser

1657
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:42,260
catastròfics

1658
00:35:42,260 --> 00:35:43,320
en l'àmbit laboral.

1659
00:35:43,860 --> 00:35:43,900
A veure,

1660
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:44,440
ens força,

1661
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:45,060
a més a més,

1662
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:46,900
a buscar múltiples perspectives

1663
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:47,400
de to

1664
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,560
o d'argumentació

1665
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:49,580
abans de prendre

1666
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:50,520
una decisió final

1667
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:51,680
i a no refiar-nos

1668
00:35:51,680 --> 00:35:53,200
mai d'una veritat absoluta

1669
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:53,740
que no estigui

1670
00:35:53,740 --> 00:35:54,840
degudament contrastada

1671
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,080
per nosaltres mateixos.

1672
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:58,080
És tot un exercici mental.

1673
00:35:58,980 --> 00:35:59,240
Llavors,

1674
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:00,480
la pregunta és inevitable.

1675
00:36:01,060 --> 00:36:02,620
Si tota aquesta interacció diària,

1676
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:03,500
hora rere hora,

1677
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,000
amb una màquina freda,

1678
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:06,020
ens està obligant,

1679
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:06,580
de facto,

1680
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,820
a exercitar de valent

1681
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:09,340
tots aquests músculs essencials

1682
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:09,920
de l'empatia cognitiva,

1683
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:11,560
de la paciència

1684
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:12,880
i de la precisió semàntica,

1685
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:13,860
ens podríem estar

1686
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:14,440
entrenant

1687
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:15,380
sense donar-nos

1688
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:16,420
en absolutament de res

1689
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:17,380
per acabar sent

1690
00:36:17,380 --> 00:36:18,360
millors comunicadors

1691
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,700
amb la resta de sers humans

1692
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:20,700
de carn i ossos?

1693
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:21,240
Uf!

1694
00:36:22,380 --> 00:36:22,720
Ostres,

1695
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:23,560
quina gran pregunta!

1696
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:25,160
Jo crec que potser sí.

1697
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:25,820
Potser,

1698
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:27,120
en el fons de tot,

1699
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:28,780
aquest geni trampós

1700
00:36:28,780 --> 00:36:29,960
dels llibres antics

1701
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,180
ens està revelant

1702
00:36:31,180 --> 00:36:31,740
molt més

1703
00:36:31,740 --> 00:36:32,480
sobre la nostra

1704
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:33,640
pròpia fragilitat

1705
00:36:33,640 --> 00:36:35,300
i les nostres presses

1706
00:36:35,300 --> 00:36:36,580
a l'hora d'entendre'ns

1707
00:36:36,580 --> 00:36:37,620
els uns amb els altres

1708
00:36:37,620 --> 00:36:38,820
a l'oficina o a casa

1709
00:36:38,820 --> 00:36:39,780
que no pas

1710
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:41,100
sobre la tecnologia en si.

1711
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:42,340
És una reflexió

1712
00:36:42,340 --> 00:36:43,100
d'aquelles que,

1713
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:43,840
sincerament,

1714
00:36:43,860 --> 00:36:44,860
conviden a ser explorades

1715
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:46,160
en profunditat

1716
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:46,820
en algun moment.

1717
00:36:47,180 --> 00:36:48,020
Em sembla molt,

1718
00:36:48,240 --> 00:36:48,800
molt encertada

1719
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:50,080
aquesta visió humanista

1720
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:50,700
del fenomen.

1721
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:51,760
Doncs ho deixem aquí

1722
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,580
com una bona idea

1723
00:36:52,580 --> 00:36:53,260
per rumiar

1724
00:36:53,260 --> 00:36:54,700
mentre la tecnologia

1725
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:55,700
inaturable

1726
00:36:55,700 --> 00:36:56,860
segueix avançant

1727
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:58,240
al seu ritme frenètic.

1728
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,360
La veritat és que

1729
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,060
ha estat un viatge

1730
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:00,860
molt revelador

1731
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:01,820
a seures avui

1732
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:02,880
intentar comprendre

1733
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:03,960
els secrets més amagats

1734
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,140
d'aquesta llanterna màgica

1735
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:05,740
tan particular

1736
00:37:05,740 --> 00:37:06,300
de la qual

1737
00:37:06,300 --> 00:37:07,060
tothom parla

1738
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:08,020
però pocs dominen.

1739
00:37:08,260 --> 00:37:09,140
He gaudit molt

1740
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:09,780
de l'anàlisi,

1741
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:10,260
de veritat.

1742
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:11,020
Un plaer.

1743
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:12,480
El plaer ha estat meu.

1744
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:13,840
Ens retrobem

1745
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:14,260
aviat

1746
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,680
per continuar analitzant

1747
00:37:15,680 --> 00:37:16,160
junts

1748
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:17,460
temes apassionants.

1749
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:18,700
Fins a la propera

1750
00:37:18,700 --> 00:37:19,580
immersió profunda.

1751
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:20,700
Cuideu-vos molt.

